Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:21.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Blackmail
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blackmail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.37,0:00:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cowardly action by which\Nsomeone demands goods or money,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.05,0:00:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or coerces someone into doing\Nsomething illegal, by way of threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.19,0:00:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is especially inexcusable when one uses a young\Nperson as a shield when making such threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today we play back a blackmail case\Nthat involved a famous soccer player.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:42.02,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If we keep mourning the passing seasons,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we can't confront the mysteries in cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi's girlfriend revealed?! There's no calming Ran's wrath!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.27,0:00:49.20,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.97,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Conan! Are you looking forward to tonight's game?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:29.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the Sunday Cup finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think'll win?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's obvious! The Tokyo Spirits,\Nbecause they got Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's scored goals in 17 games in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide's good, but I like Naoki better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Naoki hurt himself practicing a while back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he won't be able to play today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:03:00.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the offense and defense of Ramusu's Big Osaka team is better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Soccer, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.26,0:03:05.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Mouri Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you going in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need help from the detective agency, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Ryoko Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.78,0:03:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone I'd like you to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly disappeared,\Nand I didn't know what else to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a picture of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were seeing each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were seeing Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that Shin'ichi was actually—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's just a big misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's someone who looks like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake! I've even kissed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:57.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:04:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he told you he was working on a case,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he was actually fooling around with some other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, this is just a big—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't live without Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't keep on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:19.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sorry, but I've never seen you before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:22.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this girl's deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was kissing really as far as you two went?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or did you go even farther?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.58,0:04:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't answer questions like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, Mouri Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.16,0:04:37.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, Shin'ichi! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:43.02,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}About the new gadget I gave you this morning, the battery—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure thing! I'll pass the message on to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, Shin'ichi-{\i1}niichan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that Shin'ichi on the phone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said he'd call Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} later,\Nso don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get to see Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's go to her house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.60,0:05:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi might show up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.35,0:05:11.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll all go together,\Nand then I can teach him a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mind, do you, Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:15.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass. I don't care about some kids' sordid love lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll pass too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I will go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The lock has marks on it\Nfrom being tampered with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:49.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only men's and children's shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No girls live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't right. Who exactly is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where was the tea again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spoons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teapot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Akagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. How long have you been seeing Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As his childhood friend, I just have to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:23.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ryoko Akagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:30.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who does she think she is, ignoring me like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Doesn't like talking to me, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like I need to delve a little deeper into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,"Mamoru"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would seem that this is this boy's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's the person with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen him somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.17,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The National Sports Stadium is really livening up
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:11.76,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as the championship match of the Sunday Cup continues!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:13.44,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The game remains tied at 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Will the Tokyo Spirits be the first to score?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:17.33,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or will it be Big Osaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with suddenly switching the TV on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:24.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Does she hate the idea of talking to me that much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're watching soccer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} insisted on watching it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.79,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh! Another bad kick by Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.79,0:07:38.64,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is 19-year old Hideo Akagi starting to show signs of age?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Akagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:49.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha! That picture was of Hide—\NHideo Akagi from the Tokyo Spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:53.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So then Mamoru Akagi, the boy in the picture, is his little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, the magazines said\Nthat his parents died 2 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and that he lives with his brother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:03.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means that she really\Ndoesn't live here at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then why is she here? And why use a fake name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:10.57,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! Hide missed another kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's really out of form today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange... Why did he make such a simple mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.98,0:08:18.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It seemed almost intentional...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! Don't tell me this is actually...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll use the gizmo the Doc gave me this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:40.68,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is my latest invention, the Mobile Boxed Lunch Fax Machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Latest invention? Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.35,0:08:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All he did was shove a fax machine inside a boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:54.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.75,0:08:55.73,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Um, I—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a kidnapping, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The one kidnapped was Mamoru Akagi{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.51,0:09:09.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's the younger brother of Hideo Akagi,\Nwho's playing on TV right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.99,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper's demand was that he lose the game on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You said that you were going out with me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.41,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}because you wanted to get in contact with me as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I assume that the kidnapper threatened to kill Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:24.10,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}if you got the police or any detectives involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason you used the false name of Ryoko Akagi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was because you didn't want to raise suspicion from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to bring me to the Akagi home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then tell me what was really going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.11,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and then tell me what was really going on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:36.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how did you know he was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.59,0:09:44.88,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You haven't even come here yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, that's because I'm a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please write down the details about\NMamoru{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}'s kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.65,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and fax them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The number is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:09:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.61,0:10:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?!\NThat's Shin'ichi on the phone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy! Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} understood what I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the... What's she crying about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come here and explain yourself, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could swear I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm hearing my voice from the other phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:33.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means Shin'ichi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...inside this apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I found out Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was kidnapped
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I came to make him breakfast this morning."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm sending the kidnapper's letter that was on the table
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.81,0:10:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,along with the letter the kidnapper made Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} write."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:10:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Bring Mamoru back to life."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.83,0:11:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange message for someone asking for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran might actually be more difficult to handle than this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hide sets up the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! He's kicked the ball too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.29,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Has he made another bad kick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.45,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No! Luckily, Takeda is there to receive it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.25,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He fakes and shoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:41.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.34,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now that's the Hide we know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:47.23,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A brilliant play that broke through the opponent's defense!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You broke our agreement.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.71,0:12:08.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Consider your brother as good as gone."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late! Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:23.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:27.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-kun{\r\be10} is dead if I don't find the kidnapper soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This was a 3rd grader that was kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even if he put up a real struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.41,0:12:35.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}it's unnatural for his room to be this messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the Onimaru Quest game\Nthat came out yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapped kid wouldn't take a game with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.33,0:12:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Genta and Mitsuhiko mentioned something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.74,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hero actually dies during the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.38,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah! And you can't beat it without bringing him back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing him back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.24,0:13:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.90,0:13:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} used his own name for the main character's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Mamoru in that letter meant the game's main character!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who Mamoru, Hideo, and Ryoko are,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but who's this Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait. Hide and Naoki...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:42.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hide's good, but I like Naoki better!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aha! Naoki Uemura, the one\Nwho joined the Spirits last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these two marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if they were the "ki" in Naoki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:56.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've found out where Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is, Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.59,0:14:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.85,0:14:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, do you know a person\Nnamed Naoki Uemura?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course! He's Hideo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s best friend; he lives real close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:23.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tell me, does he come by often to play with Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Naoki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knows a lot about video games...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wasn't kidnapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scratches on the front door lock\Nand the ransacked bedroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit did these intentionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All to make it look like a sinister kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:45.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The full message of Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-kun{\r\be10}'s letter probably went like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}"I'm going to Naoki-{\i1}niichan{\i0}'s house so he can bring Mamoru back to life."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.38,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper tore out and used only that one part of the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then you're saying the one who took him was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThe one responsible is Naoki Uemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is at his house—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I finally, finally found you, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.25,0:15:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi! Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.07,0:15:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm using the toilet right now;\NI can't just come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tell me she's not going to use karate on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} says he wants\Nto talk to you on the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he needs to say something to me,\Nhe can say it right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.55,0:15:45.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's something important\Nthat I want only Ran to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:47.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:52.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.66,0:15:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you wanna give me more of your excuses, then fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what do you wanna tell me, Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell me, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi-{\i1}niichan{\i0} just ran outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was going to rescue Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he went to Naoki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoki's? Is that where Shin'ichi ran off to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're showing me the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.15,0:16:38.56,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! Another bad kick by Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.85,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's happened to our gifted Hideo Akagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:42.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mamoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.90,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Ryoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:52.75,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-chan{\r\be10}?! What is it? I'm kind of—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just please open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:16:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Can you let me in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.91,0:17:06.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way. My girlfriend's here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want her to get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! If you're there, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You better knock that off—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi! Come out right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to leave the house\Nwithout saying a word!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I wrote you a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! I finally beat the game\Nthanks to Naoki-{\i1}niichan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Ryoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Mamoru really alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:50.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what're you doing out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in big trouble if you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mamoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.89,0:17:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, Hide! Second half's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:08.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.55,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}2 to 1! Hide's finally in the zone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.67,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's playing like the first half was all a ruse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideo Akagi is truly gifted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:20.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gifted, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hideo's got a gift, while I'm a man of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.85,0:18:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both his popularity and salary\Nare higher than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet we had basically the same number of goals back in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I spent everyday rigorously training\Nso that I could outdo him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I finally caught up to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I surpassed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:46.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until he shattered my right leg\Nduring a practice match, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. He intentionally went for my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was afraid that I had outclassed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's put me on the sideline for 3 full months, all thanks to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:19:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible to try to surpass him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.79,0:19:04.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never had any intentions of hurting Mamoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the match, I was going to return him to his house
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then disappear somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to get back at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:14.84,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And the game is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:18.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Tokyo Spirits have won the Sunday Cup, 3 to 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:23.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our game's over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}. Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell them there was a kidnapping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Congratulations, Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.42,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who would you like to dedicate\Nthis victory to the most?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:37.86,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, I would like to dedicate it to\Nmy younger brother Mamoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:40.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but I really have to give this one to Naoki instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:43.82,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My greatest rival, Naoki Uemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.66,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After he joined the team, I started scoring more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.60,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come back soon, Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:51.12,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll be waiting for you on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's so stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.33,0:19:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hasn't even the slightest idea\Nof what I've done...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.58,0:20:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to interrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.83,0:20:10.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but where did you hide Shin'ichi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it,\Nwe haven't seen him at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want me to give him a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.76,0:20:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A call?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh oh! The cell phone's in my bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't always know it, he gave it to me today—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Of all times, why won't it open now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:45.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're there, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away this time, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal with that Ryoko girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing at her house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were working on a difficult case!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-She was just—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:03.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar! She was crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She cried when you called her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who wants to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just come out and explain it all, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.66,0:21:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it matter to you? It's my own decision to cry if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like it when you cry.{If making two lines out of this, the cut is 21:35.85}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I have to get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.87,0:21:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's not an answer! Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.83,0:21:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dr. Agasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.67,0:21:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Shin'ichi,\Nhe ran off that way while blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blushing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.46,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't like it when you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.06,0:22:03.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said too much, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look who's talking, you little coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly, honestly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.63,0:23:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Truly, honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.31,0:23:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:46.15,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No police were involved in this latest incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:50.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But Ran made Ryoko{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} explain time after time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:55.79,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...and it took 3 full days for her\Nto finally believe I was innocent.
